2FN9421Os.png&h=e101b575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到avengers 2，激光又work返<br />\n包括同vision and Thor 一齊射Ultron <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTWwU8N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTWwU8N.png&h=80570b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋同thor合作炸城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fJWmOZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fJWmOZ.png&h=bf248d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知去到CA3，激光就玩臭咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVision承襲tony嘅戰術，用粒mind stone 射射<br />\n點知殺紅了眼，射到人半身不遂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDKOcVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDKOcVN.png&h=ecddc497&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/28/115858_837ad14918761fad8d13610bed112acb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F28%2F115858_837ad14918761fad8d13610bed112acb.png&h=24da2de9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/28/115901_262070caf278691c98672c59f69c5abd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F28%2F115901_262070caf278691c98672c59f69c5abd.png&h=f1a584ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到avengers 3，又係用激光<br />\n結果仲俾人反傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjCgmPr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjCgmPr.png&h=6a1f14ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPnstur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPnstur.png&h=a34b2c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVision 哥哥，射到咁上下耐就好停啦<br />\n<br />\nTony 一開場用激光打隻大隻佬係ok的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wurtcWc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwurtcWc.png&h=f457605a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但最後tony同thanos隻抽隻<br />\nTony又係用激光死射爛射<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMFqe9Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMFqe9Y.png&h=42e79ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ma7Hhoj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fma7Hhoj.png&h=cc9ad1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大佬呀，射到咁上下好停啦，轉下手啦<br />\n<br />\nWanda用激光爆石同拖住thanos唔計<br />\n<br />\n結論: 唔亂用激光就唔洗死"},{"pid":"b1fb8fa032a92aa4903e9cbda5984134d1c445b4","tid":1129434,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:24:46.000Z","msg":"點解你老死d po先有人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d29cf60f28693a14ebdddd041a6241de249dc5","tid":1129434,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46b8b3e981e2c283a7c85c6c47c971dbf2e4ab6","tid":1129434,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T18:44:28.000Z","msg":"Tony發明iron man suit之後，早期至中期嘅激光係幾洗得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如: <br />\n佢射9個boss (iron man 1)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vt7Dz7T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVt7Dz7T.png&h=f1d0da6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同war machine一齊射爆boss ( iron man 2)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvzFOs1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvzFOs1.png&h=92cec467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有時候會亂用一下，例如同WM互射 (iron man 2)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRJvreY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRJvreY.png&h=019cf017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者用400%電力炸落去thor到，人地都只係反一反身就打返轉頭<br />\n你就反省下下下用激光掂唔掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hi0d8tr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHi0d8tr.pn